name: CRYPTO NINJAS SAIZO&SASUKE in MATSURI
description:
SAIZO and SASUKE are enjoying the Ninja Festival. 
Left Ninja : "KIRIGAKURE SAIZO"
Right Ninja : "SARUTOBI SASUKE"

SAIZO has "RINGO AME".
It is a sweet made by caulking apples.

SASUKE has "YOYO".
It is a Japanese toy that you can raise and lower by hand to play.
